{"article_id":"2uAKnwLv4Xz5xkZK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump on Tuesday fired FBI Director James Comey ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"sweeping away the man","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"who is responsible for the bureau 's investigation","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"into whether members of his campaign team colluded with Russia in its interference in last year 's election .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The bombshell announcement","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that sent shock and surprise","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"ricocheting through Washington","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"ends the career of the man","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who was once seen as the unimpeachable and nonpartisan ideal of how a law enforcement officer should behave .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"But Comey saw his reputation tarnished","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"when he was dragged into the toxic politics of the 2016 campaign .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The Trump administration attributed Comey 's dismissal to his handling of the investigation into Democratic nominee Hillary Clinton 's email server ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"but Democrats ridiculed that notion ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"raising parallels to Watergate-era firings","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and suggested","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Comey was getting too close to the White House with the Russia probe .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"In any case , senior White House officials appeared to have badly misjudged the impact of Trump 's sudden move .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"A source with knowledge of discussions inside the White House told CNN 's Dana Bash","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that the thinking was that","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"because Democrats were saying precisely what Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein said in a letter","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"explaining the grounds for Comey 's dismissal ,","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"there would be no backlash .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"What was not thought through , apparently , was an explanation","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"of why Comey was fired now , at a time","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"when critics would immediately conclude","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"it was because of the Russia probe .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"In recent days , Comey again came under fire for his handling of the investigation into Clinton 's private email server .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Many Democrats believe","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that his announcement","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that he was reopening the probe 11 days before the election","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"cost the former secretary of state the presidency .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Trump referred to Democrats ' criticism of Comey Wednesday morning ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"tweeting ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"`` The Democrats have said some of the worst things about James Comey ,","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"including the fact","depth":16},{"id":36,"text":"that he should be fired ,","depth":16},{"id":37,"text":"but now they play so sad ! ''","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"The Democrats have said some of the worst things about James Comey ,","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"including the fact","depth":15},{"id":40,"text":"that he should be fired ,","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"but now they play so sad !","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"May 10 , 2017","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Comey learned of his dismissal from televisions","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"tuned to the news ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"as he was addressing the workforce at the FBI office in Los Angeles ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"law enforcement sources said .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"The source said","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"he made a joke about it","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to lighten the mood","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"and called his office","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"to get confirmation .","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"Longtime Trump ally Roger Stone was among those","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"who recommended to the President","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"that he fire Comey ,","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"according to a source familiar with the conversation .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Stone ,","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"who also is being scrutinized by the FBI as part of its Russia investigation ,","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"spoke to Trump","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"after Comey appeared at a hearing last week on Capitol Hill ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"according to the source .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Trump immediately disputed","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that Stone was involved :","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"`` The Roger Stone report on @ CNN is false","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"- Fake News .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Have not spoken to Roger in a long time -","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"had nothing","depth":17},{"id":69,"text":"to do with my decision . '' The Roger Stone report on @ CNN is false","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"- Fake News .","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"Have not spoken to Roger in a long time -","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"had nothing","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"to do with my decision .","depth":16},{"id":74,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"May 10 , 2017","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Stone said","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he was not the source behind the reporting","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"but added","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that he supported the firing of Comey `` 100 % . ''","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"A White House spokesperson reached out to CNN","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"to reiterate the President 's tweet","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"that he has not spoken to Stone in a `` long time , ''","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"adding ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"`` The President has not spoken to Roger Stone in many months","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"and any reports","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"suggesting otherwise","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"are categorically untrue . ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"In a signed letter","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"released by the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Trump informed Comey","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that he was `` hereby terminated and removed from office , effective immediately , ''","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"explaining","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that he reached the conclusion","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that Comey is `` not able to effectively lead the bureau . ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"`` It is essential that we find new leadership for the FBI","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that restores public trust and confidence in its vital law enforcement mission , ''","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Trump told Comey in the letter .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"`` I wish you the best of luck in your future endeavors . ''","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"White House press secretary Sean Spicer ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"sandwiched in the dark between a gaggle of reporters and a large shrub on the White House driveway ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"described Trump 's decision as arriving only after a long memo from the deputy attorney general ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Spicer said","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"was delivered Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"detailing Comey 's shortcomings","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"on investigating Clinton 's emails .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"But multiple White House officials said","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Trump had been considering firing Comey for at least a week","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"before he made Tuesday 's decision .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Indeed , Trump revealed his anger in a string of late-night messages on Twitter May 2 , exactly a week before his final decision was made public .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"At the center of Rosenstein 's rationale","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"for recommending Comey 's firing","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"was the director 's handling of the investigation into Clinton 's private server , namely his decision","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"to recommend","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"no charges be filed","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and the news conference","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"he held","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"to explain his reasoning .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Senator calls Comey firing 'shocking '","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Senator calls Comey firing 'shocking '","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"01:03","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Rosenstein accused Comey of attempting to `` usurp the attorney general 's authority ''","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"by publicly announcing","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"why he felt","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"the case should be closed","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"without prosecution .","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"`` Compounding the error ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"the director ignored another longstanding principle :","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"We do not hold press conferences","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"to release derogatory information about the subject of a declined criminal investigation , ''","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"Rosenstein argued in his memo .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"`` We should reject the departure","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"and return to the traditions","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"( of the bureau ) , ''","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"Rosenstein said .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"`` The way","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"the director handled the conclusion of the email investigation","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"was wrong .","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"As a result , the FBI is unlikely to regain public and congressional trust","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"until it has a director","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"who understands the gravity of the mistakes","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"and pledges never to repeat them . ''","depth":16},{"id":147,"text":"But Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer said","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"he told Trump on the telephone","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"that he had made a terrible mistake .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"`` Were these investigations getting too close to home for the President ? ''","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Schumer asked .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"And in a sign of possible trouble for the administration , Republican Sen. Richard Burr ,","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"who is leading a Senate intelligence committee probe into alleged Russian influence on the election ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"expressed disquiet at the firing of Comey ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"which he described as a `` loss for the bureau and the nation .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"`` I am troubled by the timing and reasoning of Director Comey 's termination .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"I have found Director Comey to be a public servant of the highest order ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"and his dismissal further confuses an already difficult investigation by the Committee , ''","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"Burr said .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"As Democrats renewed their demands for a special counsel ,","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"arguing","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that the Trump Justice Department could not be trusted to oversee the case ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Republicans insisted","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"that one was not needed .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Rod Rosenstein , the new deputy attorney general , is competent to lead that effort , ''","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"said Texas Sen. John Cornyn , a member of the GOP leadership .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"But Republican Senate Foreign Relations Committee Chairman Bob Corker of Tennessee said","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"though Rosenstein 's rationale","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"for removing Comey","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"was sound ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"it , would `` raise questions . ''","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"Sen. John McCain added :","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"`` While the President has the legal authority","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"to remove the director of the FBI ,","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"I am disappointed in the President 's decision","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"to remove James Comey from office . ''","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"The Arizona senator renewed his request for a special congressional committee","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"to review the Russia allegations .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"CNN 's senior legal analyst Jeffrey Toobin was not buying the idea","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"that Comey was sacked over the Clinton investigation ,","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"it was `` absurd . ''","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"Toobin branded the move a `` grotesque abuse of power by the President of the United States . ''","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"`` This is not something","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"that is within the American political tradition , ''","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"Toobin said ,","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"comparing the sacking of Comey to President Richard Nixon 's firing of special prosecutor Archibald Cox during the Watergate scandal .","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"`` This is not normal .","depth":14},{"id":191,"text":"This is not politics as usual , ''","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"said Toobin ,","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"though he added","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"that Trump did have the legal authority","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"to fire an FBI director .","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"The White House , however , said","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"that the impetus for the firing of Comey came from Rosenstein ,","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"that he was a career prosecutor","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"who served under President Barack Obama as the US Attorney for Maryland ,","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"and was confirmed in his new job on April 25 .","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"A senior administration official said","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"that Rosenstein assessed the situation","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"upon taking office","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"and concluded","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"the FBI director had lost his confidence .","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"He sent his recommendation to Sessions","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"-- who has recused himself from the Russia investigation","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"since he was a Trump adviser and campaign surrogate --","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"who forwarded it to Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"who accepted it on Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":213,"text":"Toobin :","depth":6},{"id":214,"text":"Trump admin going to put a stooge in","depth":6},{"id":215,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":216,"text":"MUST WATCH Toobin :","depth":6},{"id":217,"text":"Trump admin going to put a stooge in 01:26","depth":6},{"id":218,"text":"Former Clinton campaign officials accused Trump of using the furor over Comey 's handling of the email server as a ruse","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"to get out from under the Russia investigation .","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"`` I was as frustrated , concerned and disappointed as anyone with Director Comey 's handling of the email investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"but President Trump just fired the man","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"investigating how Russia meddled in our election and whether members of his campaign were involved , an investigation","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"President Trump called a `` charade '' only 24 hours ago , ''","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"said Clinton 's former campaign manager , Robby Mook .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"`` It 's equally concerning that our attorney general ,","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"who lied about his own meetings with the Russians ,","depth":10},{"id":227,"text":"approved Director Comey 's firing , ''","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"One Trump loyalist ,","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"who worked on the campaign and the transition ,","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"gave his reaction to CNN 's Jim Sciutto .","depth":8},{"id":232,"text":"`` I firmly believe","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"the Russia angle is fake news .","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"But this gives me pause , ''","depth":9},{"id":235,"text":"the person said .","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"Senior Justice Department and FBI officials said","depth":7},{"id":237,"text":"they were unaware of the Comey decision until the announcement .","depth":7},{"id":238,"text":"Officials","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"who spoke to CNN","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"they were shocked by the development .","depth":7},{"id":242,"text":"Comey 's term was due to run until 2023 .","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"The decade-long tenure was introduced","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"to shield FBI directors from being drawn into politics ,","depth":9},{"id":245,"text":"but the position is still subject to dismissal at the pleasure of the President .","depth":7},{"id":246,"text":"Comey 's last appearance on Capitol Hill last week exacerbated doubts about his position .","depth":7},{"id":247,"text":"Just before news of his dismissal broke ,","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"his office issued a statement","depth":11},{"id":249,"text":"aiming to clear up his testimony","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"that former Clinton aide Huma Abedin `` forwarded hundreds and thousands '' of emails to her husband 's laptop .","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"The note ,","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"signed by Gregory Brower , assistant director of the FBI 's Office of Congressional Affairs ,","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"clarified","depth":12},{"id":254,"text":"that the `` hundreds and thousands of emails ''","depth":13},{"id":255,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":256,"text":"Comey said","depth":15},{"id":257,"text":"were 'forwarded '' from Abedin to her husband 's email","depth":15},{"id":258,"text":"`` included emails","depth":13},{"id":259,"text":"transferred via backups as well as manual forwarding . ''","depth":13},{"id":260,"text":"The White House said","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"it would immediately launch the search for a new FBI director .","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"Deputy Director Andrew McCabe is now the acting FBI director ,","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"according to a message","depth":11},{"id":264,"text":"sent to employees by Sessions .","depth":11},{"id":265,"text":"Comey was appointed FBI director by President Barack Obama in 2013 .","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"In so doing , he elevated a Republican law enforcement veteran","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"who had been critical of the Justice Department under former President George W. Bush","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"to the top domestic investigative and surveillance organization , among the most powerful posts in the world .","depth":9},{"id":269,"text":"In the decades since former FBI Director J. Edgar Hoover , the controversial director","depth":9},{"id":270,"text":"who brought the FBI into the modern era ,","depth":9},{"id":271,"text":"law enforcement has avoided the appearance","depth":9},{"id":272,"text":"of influencing politics the way","depth":10},{"id":273,"text":"Hoover did .","depth":10},{"id":274,"text":"But Comey 's decision","depth":9},{"id":275,"text":"to thrust himself repeatedly into the 2016 election","depth":9},{"id":276,"text":"put him at odds with the FBI 's general decision","depth":9},{"id":277,"text":"to stay away from the political spotlight .","depth":9},{"id":278,"text":"Comey made the decision in July to go public with his recommendation","depth":11},{"id":279,"text":"that the Justice Department not pursue any charges against Clinton or her former staffers over her email practices as secretary of state .","depth":11},{"id":280,"text":"However , he also took the opportunity","depth":11},{"id":281,"text":"to rebuke Clinton at length as being `` extremely careless '' with sensitive information .","depth":11},{"id":282,"text":"Then-candidate Trump had talked up the investigation until this point ,","depth":10},{"id":283,"text":"at which time he and his campaign derided Comey for the `` political '' decision .","depth":10},{"id":284,"text":"Just days away from the election , Comey jumped into the race again .","depth":10},{"id":285,"text":"He informed Congress , via letter ,","depth":13},{"id":286,"text":"that the FBI had reopened its investigation into Clinton .","depth":13},{"id":287,"text":"The decision was made","depth":13},{"id":288,"text":"because of its investigation into former Rep. Anthony Weiner ,","depth":14},{"id":289,"text":"who is married to Clinton confidant Huma Abedin .","depth":14},{"id":290,"text":"Comey followed up days later with another letter ,","depth":12},{"id":291,"text":"informing Congress","depth":13},{"id":292,"text":"that the FBI did n't find anything","depth":14},{"id":293,"text":"and continued to believe","depth":15},{"id":294,"text":"Clinton 's practices did not merit the pursuance of any criminal charges .","depth":15},{"id":295,"text":"After Clinton 's loss , former President Bill Clinton blamed Comey for it ,","depth":11},{"id":296,"text":"as have many Clinton staffers , at least in part .","depth":11},{"id":297,"text":"Last week , Hillary Clinton herself told CNN 's Christiane Amanpour :","depth":12},{"id":298,"text":"`` I was on the way to winning","depth":13},{"id":299,"text":"until a combination of Jim Comey 's letter on October 28 and Russian WikiLeaks raised doubts in the minds of people","depth":14},{"id":300,"text":"who were inclined to vote for me","depth":15},{"id":301,"text":"and got scared off . ''","depth":15},{"id":302,"text":"After taking office ,","depth":13},{"id":303,"text":"Trump met with Comey at the White House .","depth":13},{"id":304,"text":"`` Oh , here 's Jim , ''","depth":14},{"id":305,"text":"Trump said in January .","depth":14},{"id":306,"text":"`` He 's become more famous than me . ''","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":613,"left":0,"right":612,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":612,"left":517,"right":611,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":517,"left":337,"right":516,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":337,"left":317,"right":336,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":317,"left":310,"right":316,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":1,"right":309,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":2,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":316,"left":314,"right":315,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":312,"right":313,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":312,"left":5,"right":311,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":336,"left":321,"right":335,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":12,"right":320,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":320,"left":1